  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 292bca25009c3b846973697c392c826a, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0358eca1d351f540a61dc689202b2b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "C\u2019est pas possible ! J\u2019perds jamais aux cartes, et encore moins
      contre quelqu\u2019un d\u2019moins exp\xE9riment\xE9.\r\n"
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0358eca1d351f540a61dc689202b2b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Qu\u2019est ce qui te fait dire que j\u2019ai moins d'exp\xE9rience ? Tu ne
      sais rien de moi"
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 292bca25009c3b846973697c392c826a, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 368af27e801a8f643a3763179d93db07, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "C\u2019est pas un truc de filles c\u2019est tout."
